      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 280,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Must Have\n\nA thing is not a node unless it has these:\n\n- `id`\n- `type`\n- `position`\n- something renderable or viewable\n- a stable way for graph/editor infrastructure to identify and measure it",
